Package: gasper
Type: Package
Title: Graph Signal Processing in R
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Basile de Loynes, Fabien Navarro and Baptiste Olivier
Maintainer: Fabien Navarro <fabien.navarro@math.cnrs.fr>
Description: Graph Signal Processing in R. It provides 
    the standard operations for signal processing on graphs: 
    Graph Fourier Transform, Spectral Graph Wavelet Transform, 
    visualization tools. It also implements a data driven method
    for graph signal denoising.
License: LGPL (>= 2)
